fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 ended flat at 18,118.30. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, rose 0.29% to 13.66. Reliance Industries (RIL), ICICI Bank and Tata Motors were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The January 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 25 January 2023.
